KIBBE, Respondent, v. BRIXEY, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. February 16, 1894.) .Action by William C. Kibbe against William R. Brixey. .

Argued before VAN BRUNT, P. X, and O’BRIEN arid FOLLETT, JJ.

)I. L. Hill, for appellant.

No opinion. Order reversed and motion granted, without costs to either •party; the amended answer tendered to be served within five days after notice of order to be entered upon this decision;
